About Us

eLuminous Technologies is an India based company that provides Offshore Software development, Application Development, Web Design and Web Development solutions to clients in USA, Europe and around the globe. Our strategic offshore location, extensive experience along with following world class development standards and methodologies allows us to keep our costs reasonable and deliver best services for your outsourcing needs in areas like Web Design, Web Development, E-Commerce and Application Development.

Our Mission

We are committed to develop world class customized IT Solutions for businesses across the globe that will help them in improving efficiencies by combining individual skill sets of our team and providing our customers 24x7 support.

Our Vision

To be a world class customized IT solution provider organization with branches across the globe and developing various products under eLuminous brand which will achieve 100% growth every year.
